":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"遲d Kabylake 好似局你用Windows 10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460bff7f170fbfb6b5dc004518a8999a99700427","tid":61241,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:58:23.000Z","msg":"有時覺得好撚煩,諗緊係咪不如升撚左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c707e7d621abcd09c0e6e414a95e38e5bb4face4","tid":61241,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時覺得好撚煩,諗緊係咪不如升撚左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換左ssd (如果你識的話) 咪當clean install."},{"pid":"2b7214a0c3c865ecaca4be20aa5e88e81597554e","tid":61241,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時覺得好撚煩,諗緊係咪不如升撚左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換左ssd (如果你識的話) 咪當clean install.</blockquote><br />\n1.其實ssd用hd個分別除左開機快仲有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\n2.但係而家自動升級個windows唔係係返完本個drive度升咩,而家先換ssd有用嗎?<br />\n點樣可以做到clean install?"},{"pid":"fd7941fbc2d48737f0b3fc131d38e42dd73113bb","tid":61241,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時覺得好撚煩,諗緊係咪不如升撚左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換左ssd (如果你識的話) 咪當clean install.</blockquote><br />\n1.其實ssd用hd個分別除左開機快仲有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\n2.但係而家自動升級個windows唔係係返完本個drive度升咩,而家先換ssd有用嗎?<br />\n點樣可以做到clean install?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 好多時Windows 愈用愈慢, 因為file 愈黎愈多, 而傳統harddisk 讀取零散file 既速度係好撚慢, 所以需要做磁碟重組或者重新安裝windows.<br />\n<br />\nSsd 因為速度高好多倍, 無論讀寫大型file 或零散file 都比harddisk 快好那多, 所以理論上幾年後都唔覺得好慢<br />\n<br />\nSsd 缺點..貴..size相對細....死既時候冇得restore<br />\n雖則有以上缺點, 但速度實在太緊要, 緊要到用過返唔到轉頭, 我仍然會用ssd<br />\n<br />\n2. 其實宜家冇左免費升級, 但都有個灰色位比你upgrade.<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有幾個方法你可以參考下<br />\n<br />\n1. 買windows 10 買ssd<br />\nClean install to new ssd<br />\n<br />\n2. 買ssd upgrade windows 10<br />\nSsd 有software 可以 clone 你個windows<br />\n然後用灰色方法upgrade windows 10<br />\n<br />\n3. 買ssd keep windows 7<br />\nClone windows 7 ony"},{"pid":"d0f27d229c363808590b83cc7b8bd8de5fb0c623","tid":61241,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"用灰色方法<br />\n<a href=\"http://walker-a.com/archives/3788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwalker-a.com%2Farchives%2F3788&d=4ceTsdemY24qG2ALKXKKgZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=2cb90ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://walker-a.com/archives/3788</a>"},{"pid":"28943258ec6282363fd218c2f83adaa8302055b1","tid":61241,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時覺得好撚煩,諗緊係咪不如升撚左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n換左ssd (如果你識的話) 咪當clean install.</blockquote><br />\n1.其實ssd用hd個分別除左開機快仲有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\n2.但係而家自動升級個windows唔係係返完本個drive度升咩,而家先換ssd有用嗎?<br />\n點樣可以做到clean install?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.開機開程式咩都快<br />\n<br />\n2.你up完佢server會認左你部機，所以換ssd都可以clean install,上官網down個windows 10 media creation tool整iso入落usb到裝就得"},{"pid":"edce947ca289878460f16a3553f418c7137ceb9a","tid":61241,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"7for sure <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNote7柒左iPhone7柒埋，得win7先係神枱級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30ef28563067310d5e7f7628556632ae143b8fe","tid":61241,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"其實仲有免費Up Win10<br />\nAssistive Technology <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbe82ba0c512ac02cbff5cccba6030677a9ab57","tid":61241,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"新cpu新chipset焗鳩你用win10"},{"pid":"680e7fdb61405628d001187c747087a915b572ba","tid":61241,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"而家畫面,呢個係咪免費升級<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u2jb9i5s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu2jb9i5s&h=4e5d8429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣升,之前裝左個d野會唔會有bugs"},{"pid":"cc37ec373f294ec9e9b25dab99785cff53b894cd","tid":61241,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家畫面,呢個係咪免費升級<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u2jb9i5s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu2jb9i5s&h=4e5d8429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣升,之前裝左個d野會唔會有bugs</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難講, 其實又唔洗驚<br />\nUpgrade完 一個月內可以roll back 番wimdows 7"},{"pid":"9d0f89ebeb407aa858e75fd1118e0bc7ff6d3bdb","tid":61241,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"岩岩升左上WINDOW10 ,有咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ae1a8d352f6324a4d30c7d10045f7d923dccc5","tid":61241,"uid":30845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"Windows 10 連基本嘅熄機都有問題，有時熄完會幫你開番機"},{"pid":"557127bc7b0e106d7c7c2119e3fced7eb06272f9","tid":61241,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩係10仔DL左個ig apps,但係用唔到facebook登入,呢d係咪bugs....."},{"pid":"1e1ebe7e3426acd8b6e5a7b3deecabce6d438d7e","tid":61241,"uid":70344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:37:35.000Z","msg":"屌,原來而家得10日時間比你roll back......岩岩係設定度睇到"},{"pid":"ebaab2fb1b635c4bcda73ee189be6a6713